OL,3,CNominate your local fundraisers for
OL,4,Cthe Daily Mirror Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAwards
OL,7,FOn the night, so called "ordinary"
OL,8,Fpeople are thanked for their "extra-
OL,9,Fordinary" contribution - owning the
OL,10,Fred carpet with an array of
OL,11,Fcelebrities who come to pay their own
OL,12,Ftributes.
OL,14,FAmong them, fundraisers who don't seek
OL,15,Fthe limelight are rightly given the
OL,16,Fcredit they deserve on a national
OL,17,Fstage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
