OL,3,CNominate your local fundraisers for
OL,4,Cthe Daily Mirror Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAwards
OL,7,FSo if you know an individual or group
OL,8,Fwhose selfless fund-raising work has
OL,9,Fchanged lives for the better, now's
OL,10,Fthe time to let us know.
OL,12,FTo nominate, all you have to do is go
OL,13,Fto the ITV Website.
OL,15,FYou can nominate individuals or
OL,16,Fgroups, but only one person plus a
OL,17,Fguest can attend the Pride of Britain
OL,18,FAwards in London.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
