OL,3,CNominate your local fundraisers for
OL,4,Cthe Daily Mirror Pride of Britain
OL,5,CAwards
OL,7,FNominees must be aged 18 or over and
OL,8,Fbe available to be filmed and have
OL,9,Ftheir fundraising story told on ITV
OL,10,FRegional News.
OL,12,FComplete the nomination form and tell
OL,13,Fus why your nominee(s) deserve this
OL,14,Faward. If you are under the age of 18
OL,15,Fplease get permission from a parent or
OL,16,Fguardian before you nominate.
OL,18,FNominations close Sunday 2 August 2026
OL,19,Fat 11.59pm.
